The '''Chance Castle''' was an ancient and one of the largest hotel-[[Casino/Legends|casinos]] on [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]]. When [[Xaverri]] came to Nar Shaddaa, her shows were held at the Castle. When news of an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] attack came to Nar Shaddaa, the Castle willingly allowed [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Mako Spince]] to use their auditorium for a [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] meeting to plan for the defense of Nar Shaddaa, as an attack would be bad for business. It had a fifty story atrium. [[Bria Tharen]], disguised as [[Bria Tharen|Bria Lavval]], integrated a booking there as a [[Musician/Legends|singer]] as part of her cover story.

